A City of Cape Town official could find himself in hot water after commenting on a EFF Malema video, And agreed with the EFF Leader that he does not care about white people. Malema‚ leader of the Economic Freedom Fighters‚ warns white South-Africans: “We don’t care about your white feelings”. The facebook user Mzamo Mahlahlane Papiyana was warned by social media page admin to remove his comment but challenged the request and promised to be promoted if he could be “exposed” below is the comments made by Mzamo 